data.description: Welcome to this spacious home featuring a cozy fireplace, ideal for those chilly nights. The master bedroom boasts a walk-in closet for ample storage. Flexible living spaces offer versatility for any lifestyle. The primary bathroom includes a separate tub and shower, as well as double sinks and good under sink storage. Step outside to the fenced backyard with a serene sitting area. Partial flooring replacement in some areas adds a fresh touch. Don't miss out on this fantastic property.
